00:04:22.710 --> 00:04:30.400 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Ed Piskor: I think that -- I was
born in 1982, and the people who are

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:35.760
around my age, a little
older, a little younger,

00:04:35.760 --> 00:04:37.060
