go to the grocery store with Mom,

00:04:46.200 --> 00:04:49.240
and there would be a couple of
spinner racks at the grocery store,

00:04:49.240 --> 00:04:53.530
and I could just choose a
couple of Spider Man comics,

00:04:53.530 --> 00:04:55.900
X-Men comics, whatever they had.

00:04:55.900 --> 00:04:58.090
You could almost be
guaranteed to not be able

00:04:58.090 --> 00:05:00.480
to get two consecutive
issues of anything.

00:05:00.480 --> 00:05:01.780
&gt;&gt; Damon Locks: Exactly.

00:05:01.780 --> 00:05:03.320
&gt;&gt; Ed Piskor: Because
it was very sporadic,

00:05:03.320 --> 00:05:07.490
