probably have this similar answer.

00:05:11.380 --> 00:05:13.730
So I've always known comics.

00:05:13.730 --> 00:05:17.510
When I was a kid, it
was definitely a stack

00:05:17.510 --> 00:05:20.050
that I had that I didn't buy.

00:05:20.050 --> 00:05:22.540
It's almost like my Dad was
preparing for me to like,

00:05:22.540 --> 00:05:23.840
"Ah, kids read comic books."

00:05:23.840 --> 00:05:27.560
So while they were buying
onesies and stuff, he was stacking

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:32.860
up some comics for the future
whenever I was old enough

00:05:32.860 --> 00:05:34.960
to start reading or whatever.

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:36.870
But always read comics.

00:05:36.870 --> 00:05:41.490
Reading the Marvel and D.C.
stuff, what was really cool

00:05:41.490 --> 00:05:46.990
