Knight Returns to just --

00:08:55.900 --> 00:08:57.200
&gt;&gt; Damon Locks: So you copied?

00:08:57.200 --> 00:08:59.420
That was your way of learning
by copying the whole thing?

00:08:59.420 --> 00:09:00.720
&gt;&gt; Ed Piskor: Yeah, for sure.

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:02.020
And I had my mother letter it

00:09:02.020 --> 00:09:03.510
because her hand lettering
was nicer,

00:09:03.510 --> 00:09:06.570
