00:12:18.200 --> 00:12:19.500
&gt;&gt; Ed Piskor: 55 cents.

00:12:19.500 --> 00:12:20.800
&gt;&gt; Damon Locks: Exactly.

00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:22.950
But I have a question
