00:12:22.950 --> 00:12:24.250
&gt;&gt; Ed Piskor: Yes.

00:12:24.250 --> 00:12:25.550 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Damon Locks: Is that something --

00:12:25.550 --> 00:12:30.150
okay, so when I used to try to
