something in our brain that's kind

00:13:19.580 --> 00:13:22.120
of attuned to pattern
recognition and stuff like that.

00:13:22.120 --> 00:13:25.660
So on an intuitive sense, I think
if you look at comics long enough,

00:13:25.660 --> 00:13:29.860
