six months old.

00:18:04.530 --> 00:18:05.870
It would be considered played out,

00:18:05.870 --> 00:18:08.710
and I would just keep
digging back further.

00:18:08.710 --> 00:18:11.260
I had this impulse to just
keep digging back further,

00:18:11.260 --> 00:18:15.220
