you listening to that old stuff?

00:18:15.220 --> 00:18:17.390
My Dad has a Grandmaster
Flash record.

00:18:17.390 --> 00:18:19.010
Like that's not cool."

00:18:19.010 --> 00:18:20.500
&gt;&gt; Damon Locks: Okay.

00:18:20.500 --> 00:18:22.800
So what made you decide
you were going

00:18:22.800 --> 00:18:25.300
