greater than most cartoonists,

00:19:17.010 --> 00:19:19.770
and I have the willingness
to do the homework to figure

00:19:19.770 --> 00:19:21.070
out the stuff I don't know.

00:19:21.070 --> 00:19:23.040
So I just -- all of a sudden
