00:21:21.010 --> 00:21:22.310
&gt;&gt; Ed Piskor: Yeah.

00:21:22.310 --> 00:21:23.610
&gt;&gt; Damon Locks: You know?

00:21:23.610 --> 00:21:24.910
Oral history, you know?

00:21:24.910 --> 00:21:26.210
But have you taken oral history --

