00:21:46.680 --> 00:21:51.300
&gt;&gt; Ed Piskor: As I said, I put this
work on that BoingBoing website.

00:21:51.300 --> 00:21:54.470
They were goodly [phonetic
spelling] enough to allow me

00:21:54.470 --> 00:21:59.920 position:56%
