00:23:29.920 --> 00:23:31.220
&gt;&gt; Damon Locks: Just
have to keep going.

00:23:31.220 --> 00:23:34.860
&gt;&gt; Ed Piskor: 4.5 years
of just putting

00:23:34.860 --> 00:23:39.990
